<div id='pop' class="list_new_page_wrap do_create_ticheng_window">
  <div class="list_new_page">
    <h3>
      <label class="font-14">新建提成方案</label>
      <span class="font-18 do_cancel_create_list">✕</span>
    </h3>

    <div class="float-left plan">
      <span class="num">1</span>

      <div class="plan_name">
        <label>方案名称</label>
        <input type="text">
      </div>

      <div class="object">
        <label>适用对象</label>
        <select>
          <option>销售</option>
          <option>技师</option>
          <option>其他</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <div class="commission_coverage">
        <label>提成范围</label>
        <select>
          <option>班组</option>
          <option>个人</option>
        </select>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="ticheng float-left">
      <span class="num">2</span>
      <div class="ticheng_sel">
        <label>标准提成<input type="radio" name="ticheng_sel" checked></label>
        <label>阶梯提成<input type="radio" name="ticheng_sel"></label>
        <label>分段提成<input type="radio" name="ticheng_sel"></label>
      </div>

      <div class="regular_ticheng do_ticheng_setting" style="display:block;">
        <p class="line-height-25">标准提成定义为：</p>
        <p class="line-height-25 margin-bottom-15">无论销售数量或者施工数量为多少，只按每件固定的金额或百分点进行提成，并进行累计，请在第三步进行详细设置。</p>

        <label>提成源</label>

        <select>
          <option>金额</option>
          <option>百分比</option>
        </select>

        <label>提成形式</label>
        <select>
          <option>商品或服务的毛利</option>
        </select>

        <label>输入数量</label>
        <input type="text">
      </div>

      <div class="ladder_ticheng do_ticheng_setting" style="display:none;">
        <p class="line-height-25 margin-left-36">阶梯提成定义为：</p>
        <p class="line-height-25 margin-left-36 margin-bottom-15 width-300">提成基数按阶梯状递增，每个阶段数量溢出，则按设定的基数</p>

        <div class="setting">
          <ul class="lists_header">
            <li>#</li>
            <li>完成数</li>
            <li>提成源</li>
            <li>形式</li>
            <li>数量</li>
            <li><span class="new_list cursor-pointer">+</span></li>
          </ul>

          <div class="lists_content">
            {% for i in (1..3) %}
            <ul>
              <li class="sequence_num">1</li>
              <li><input type="text" class="width-20" name="numstart"> - <input type="text" class="width-20" name="numend"></li>
              <li>
                <select>
                  <option>金额</option>
                  <option>百分比</option>
                </select>
              </li>
              <li>
                <select class="width-120">
                  <option>商品或服务的毛利</option>
                </select>
              </li>
              <li><input type="text" class="width-40" name="profit"></li>
              <li><span class="delete delete_list cursor-pointer">×</span></li>
            </ul>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="period_ticheng do_ticheng_setting" style="display:none;">
        <p class="line-height-25 margin-left-36">分段提成定义为：</p>
        <p class="line-height-25 margin-left-36 margin-bottom-15 width-300">提成分为几个阶段的基数进行不同金额的提成，互相不累计。</p>

        <div class="setting">
          <ul class="lists_header">
            <li>#</li>
            <li>完成数</li>
            <li>提成源</li>
            <li>形式</li>
            <li>数量</li>
            <li><span class="new_list cursor-pointer">+</span></li>
          </ul>

          <div class="lists_content">
            {% for i in (1..3) %}
            <ul>
              <li class="sequence_num">1</li>
              <li><input type="text" class="width-20" name="numstart"> - <input type="text" class="width-20" name="numend"></li>
              <li>
                <select>
                  <option>金额</option>
                  <option>百分比</option>
                </select>
              </li>
              <li>
                <select class="width-120">
                  <option>商品或服务的毛利</option>
                </select>
              </li>
              <li><input type="text" class="width-40" name="profit"></li>
              <li><span class="delete delete_list cursor-pointer">×</span></li>
            </ul>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <input type="button" class="btn save_btn float-right do_save_new_list_btn" value="保存">

  </div>
</div>

